title: Nigerian election results trickle in as Peter Obi lands surprise win in Lagos
description: Nigeria's third force candidate Peter Obi has won Lagos State, according to results announced from the state's collation center.

title: Brexit deal on Northern Ireland nears as King Charles welcomes EU chief von der Leyen at Windsor
description: King Charles III is set to meet the European Commission president on Monday as Britain and the EU work to finally reach an agreement on trade rules in Northern Ireland -- a thorny and sensitive issue that has fueled post-Brexit tensions in Europe and on the island of Ireland.
